{"id":938239746,"lang":"cpp","lang_name":"C++","time":"3 weeks, 1 day","timestamp":1682223926,"status":10,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"422 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/938239746/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Sliding Subarray Beauty","memory":"185.7 MB","code":"class Solution {\npublic:\n    vector<int> getSubarrayBeauty(vector<int>& nums, int k, int x) {\n        int n = nums.size();\n        vector<int> ans, freq(51, 0);\n        for(int i=0, j=0;i<n;i++){\n            if(nums[i]<0) freq[abs(nums[i])]++;\n            if(i-j+1 >= k){\n                int count = 0;\n                for(int l=50;l>=1;l--){\n                    count += freq[l];\n                    if(count>=x){\n                        ans.push_back(-l);\n                        break;  \n                    } \n                }\n                if(count<x) ans.push_back(0);\n                if(nums[j]<0) freq[abs(nums[j])]--;\n                j++;\n            }\n        }\n        return ans;\n    }\n};","compare_result":"","title_slug":"sliding-subarray-beauty","has_notes":false}
